H0.text: In the British military, a bombadier is equivalent to which other rank. Sergeant

H1.text: In the British military, a bombadier is equivalent to which other rank. Lance Corporal

H2.text: In the British military, a bombadier is equivalent to which other rank. Corporal

H3.text: In the British military, a bombadier is equivalent to which other rank. Cpl.

A4.text: Bombardier is today equivalent to the rank of corporal in other branches.

A5.text: Unlike a lance corporal, a bombardier, who was junior to a corporal, held full non-commissioned rank and not an acting appointment.
